snippet.title: LISA: The UNDONE Release Teaser
snippet.description:
That's right, it's done. It's out. You can finally play it.
Lisa: The Undone Part One is now free and released for everybody to play!

Gamejolt Link:
https://gamejolt.com/games/dreamsofstars/696084
Itch.io Link:
https://redisco.itch.io/lisa-the-undone

I am very proud to show all of you the work we've managed to do these past few years. I hope you enjoy.
Sincerely, have a good time.

My Twitter:
https://twitter.com/SeriousRedGuy
